dct_title_s: Insurance maps of the New Jersey coast : volume 1 (Overview)
dct_description_sm: Includes key, key maps, index to sheet numbers, and text. Series includes maps of Atlantic Highlands, Highland Beach, Highlands of Navesink, Long Branch, Monmouth Beach, Navesink Beach, Seabright and Seaside. Title sheet; map sheets foldered separately under name of town.
dct_publisher_sm: New York : Sanborn-Perris Map Co., Limited, 1890.
